"An internal shared memory filesystem is used for System V shared memory "
"(B<shmget>(2))  and shared anonymous mappings (B<mmap>(2)  with the "
"B<MAP_SHARED> and B<MAP_ANONYMOUS> flags).  This filesystem is available "
